Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So yeah, that’s basically what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, so that baby with the bib \Nwasn’t your secret child, Pastel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not, Madoka! \NI’m still in middle school, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just, when that kid said \N“mama,” I totally thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if you think about it, there’s no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,0:00:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you don’t even have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well… yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:51.32,Song,,0,0,0,,{FantasianーパラダイスMIX-\N歌:國府田マリ子\N作詞:WINBEE\N作曲: コナミ矩形波倶楽部\N編曲:光田健一}{full lyrics from marty's booklet: 煌めく星屑のペイブメント\NあなたへとつづくBLUE WAVE\N瞬く永遠のディスタンス\N月あかり 潮風が髪にふれて\Nさあ ファンタジアン 教えてね恋の手ほどきを\Nねえ わたしから 羽ばたく前のレジェンド受け止めて\N彷徨う幻想のラビリンス\Nためらいも勇気に変わる\N夢見るやすらぎのテンダネス\N目を醒ます精霊たちも ほら頰寄せ\Nさあ ファンタジアン はじまるわ恋のプロローグ\Nねえ あなたとの 星降る夜のロマンス抱きしめて\Nさあ ファンタジアン 教えてね 恋の手ほどきを\Nねえ わたしから 羽ばたく前のレジェンド受け止めて\Nいつまでもつづいてね恋のシルエット\Nねえ あなたとの 潮騒香るバカンス感じてる\N煌めく星屑のペイブメント\N月影 揺らめいて歩いていく\N瞬く永遠のディスタンス\Nあなたとどこまでも二人きりでいたい} Shimmering stardust pavement
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.31,Song,,0,0,0,,A blue wave leading me to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:06.29,Song,,0,0,0,,Everlasting twinkling distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:16.79,Song,,0,0,0,,Moonlight and sea breeze brush against my hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:28.51,Song,,0,0,0,,Come now, Fantasian, teach me the ways of love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:43.27,Song,,0,0,0,,Hey, before I spread my wings, receive this legend from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:12.84,Song,,0,0,0,,A wandering labyrinth of fantasy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:13.66,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:18.51,Song,,0,0,0,,Even hesitation turns into courage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:21.53,Song,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H840F00&}Even hesitation {probably?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:23.02,Song,,0,0,0,,A dreaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve already decided on it, though. {??? this sore iyuu sounds like "That thing" but later she totally makes that sound like the actual name of her future child, or am I trippin?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,On what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My future baby’s name. \NIt's gotta be a good name, doesn't it? {there, she says "don't you think it's a good name?" as if she said it to pastel already but i have no idea what she's on about}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... Wow, you’ve actually\Nthought that far ahead, Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don’t want to panic when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.02,0:01:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, you need to find a wonderful guy. {darling}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Same goes for both of us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A crustacean... of some sort? {crabs and such}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like some rare species of crab. {?????????}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Pastel forget this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:47.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I left it on purpose! \NGo on, pick it up and take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm… I’ve never seen anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it tastes like…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:56.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,Geez, Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:02:01.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,Even if it was a misunderstanding, you definitely\Ndidn't have to spread those rumors around school
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:04.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,that I had a child during my time on Venus… {meaning what happens now is her vengeance}{parenthood; parent or someone with children on the way (esp. an expecting mother)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah… it's Pastel's fault for forgetting them here. I'm not doing anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:19.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,No! It's all your fault{[for spreading rumors]}. Now then, \Nenjoy this little taste of a Venusian threat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:23.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ah! I even feel kinda rude doing this. {mean/unkind}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes… {????}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,She ate it! {????}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My {\i1}god,{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}was that good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing! What is this?! \NWhat is this?! It’s so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:49.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:56.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,What is Madoka, really... {kind of creature}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:59.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,
